23 housing benefits. As a part of this plan, the Department of Commerce, the
24 Housing Finance Agency, and all local housing authorities established under
25 Chapter 157 of the General Statutes shall develop a method for verifying the
26 immigration status of applicants for publicly funded housing benefits who are
27 noncitizens prior to the initiation of benefits.
